05:13.143 --> 05:14.636
That's as good as it gets.

05:26.535 --> 05:27.757
Don't waste your time.

05:42.625 --> 05:43.629
Ms. Tobey,

05:44.403 --> 05:45.777
would you come with us, please?

05:48.600 --> 05:49.404
Harmon.

05:49.841 --> 05:50.556
Harmon...

05:51.280 --> 05:52.379
sam...

05:52.566 --> 05:53.786
what's this all about?

05:53.949 --> 05:56.238
Ms. Tobey, I'm placing you under arrest.

05:56.432 --> 05:57.391
Arrest?

05:58.399 --> 05:59.048
For what?

05:59.305 --> 06:00.203
Child abuse.

06:00.695 --> 06:02.310
Oh, my god. What...

06:20.804 --> 06:25.834
<i>So long ago, another life</i>

06:25.922 --> 06:29.822
<i>I can feel your heart beat</i>

06:30.304 --> 06:35.160
<i>it's not a dream remember us</i>

06:35.529 --> 06:39.416
<i>I can see it in your eyes</i>

06:39.424 --> 06:42.928
<i>we'll find our place in time</i>

06:42.939 --> 06:47.556
<i>our place in time beyond the sun</i>

06:48.566 --> 06:52.461
<i>we'll find our place in time</i>

06:52.473 --> 06:57.527
