07:23.000 --> 07:27.500
I've got to accept the fact that he's 
gonna screw up like a teenager.

07:27.800 --> 07:29.000
He'll learn from his mistakes.

07:29.100 --> 07:31.200
Get it out of his system.

07:31.300 --> 07:33.400
But shawn...

07:33.500 --> 07:35.500
it's been a year.

07:35.800 --> 07:38.400
How could he cut us out like that?

07:38.500 --> 07:41.800
And danny. He's eating himself up inside.

07:41.900 --> 07:44.500
He used to be such a sweet boy.

07:45.400 --> 07:47.900
Yeah. I remember what pop used to say...

07:48.000 --> 07:49.100
"you think you've got problems?

07:49.200 --> 07:51.500
Wait till you become a parent.

07:52.100 --> 07:54.200
Little did we know.

07:54.300 --> 07:55.600
Yeah.

07:55.700 --> 07:57.900
What do you want to bet they're talking about us downstairs?

07:58.000 --> 07:59.800
That's what they live for.

07:59.900 --> 08:03.000
If they didn't have us to worry about. They'd die of boredom.

08:03.300 --> 08:05.000
I've seen you around campus.

08:05.100 --> 08:06.600
I saw you too.

08:06.700 --> 08:08.600
Why didn't you say something?

08:08.700 --> 08:10.300
It's been. Like. Four years.

08:10.400 --> 08:11.300
