08:11.400 --> 08:13.900
"Welcome back from coma worid"?

08:15.200 --> 08:16.800
I don't know. I guess

08:16.900 --> 08:18.900
seeing you reminded me of shawn.

08:19.000 --> 08:21.200
You two were always so tight.

08:21.300 --> 08:23.300
