08:23.400 --> 08:25.700
"where you going? Can I come too?"

08:25.800 --> 08:28.200
I thought you guys were so cool.

08:28.900 --> 08:31.600
I was 14.What did I know?

08:35.299 --> 08:37.600
Mom says you talked to him?

08:38.400 --> 08:40.900
I don't think he heard me.

08:41.000 --> 08:42.600
You know.

08:44.000 --> 08:46.100
