08:46.200 --> 08:48.200
stealing nikki.

08:48.300 --> 08:49.900
Running out on us the way he did.

08:50.000 --> 08:52.000
Breaking mom's heart.

08:52.800 --> 08:54.800
But it wasn't his fault.

08:56.000 --> 08:59.300
