decided to make everything beautiful and kicked us out.

09:58.100 --> 09:59.000
It's okay. You can let 'em go.

09:59.100 --> 10:00.600
They were stealing food.

10:00.700 --> 10:02.600
Well. Last time I checked. The food was free.

10:02.700 --> 10:03.600
Don't make me pull rank.

10:03.700 --> 10:04.700
Come on.

10:04.800 --> 10:05.700
Yes. Sir. Mr. Farrell.

10:05.800 --> 10:06.410
Thank you.

10:09.200 --> 10:10.600
Big shot. Huh?

10:10.700 --> 10:12.300
I'm impressed.

10:12.400 --> 10:14.000
I'm really sorry that we trashed your home.

10:14.100 --> 10:15.000
I am.

10:15.100 --> 10:16.400
