10:16.500 --> 10:20.800
It's a hell of a lot warmer here than
 crashing near l-90 bridge.

10:21.200 --> 10:23.000
Food's still free. Right?

10:23.100 --> 10:24.200
Yes. Absolutely.

10:24.300 --> 10:25.500
Please be my guest.

10:25.600 --> 10:27.400
Yeah. We will.

10:29.000 --> 10:31.200
Protect the future. Huh?

10:31.300 --> 10:33.700
Got to have one first.

