10:45.400 --> 10:47.200
Isn't your sister with her?

10:47.300 --> 10:49.500
The one with all the tattoos?

10:50.000 --> 10:51.100
Sorry.

10:51.200 --> 10:55.100
Those beer kegs kyle ordered 
should be showing up right about now.

10:55.200 --> 10:57.300
Yeah. You read these charges?

10:57.400 --> 11:00.200
"Teacher is accused of reckless endangerment.

11:00.300 --> 11:03.200
Placing her students' health. Welfare. 
And safety at risk.

11:03.300 --> 11:04.900
"Could that be any more vague?

11:05.000 --> 11:08.600
Well. That could be anything from grabbing them 
on the arms to touching them on the privates.

11:08.700 --> 11:10.500
Or maybe she did nothing.

11:10.600 --> 11:13.000
Yeah."Nothing" would be my vote.

11:13.100 --> 11:15.600
A 4400 serial killer was bad enough.

11:15.700 --> 11:18.400
But a 4400 child molester?

11:23.100 --> 11:24.500
You're damn right we don't want her back!

11:24.600 --> 11:25.800
Not now. Not ever.

11:25.900 --> 11:26.900
Look.

11:27.000 --> 11:28.700
I don't know what's going to happen with ms. Tobey.

11:28.800 --> 11:29.600
She's out on bail. Right?

11:29.700 --> 11:30.000
That's right.

11:30.100 --> 11:32.095
And her bond was paid by
parents from this school.

11:32.096 --> 11:33.400
Yeah. And if they're not worried about their kids.

11:33.500 --> 11:34.500
Then we'll worry for them.

11:34.600 --> 11:36.000
Ask sal here. He'll tell you.

11:36.100 --> 11:37.100
His kid was abused.

11:37.200 --> 11:39.100
Same as melinda and teddy.

11:39.200 --> 11:40.500
What about your child. Mr...

11:40.600 --> 11:42.700
Venner. Frank venner.

11:42.800 --> 11:44.600
It's not like she didn't try with my boy.

11:44.700 --> 11:46.500
Greg just happened to be one of the lucky ones.

11:46.600 --> 11:47.300
Tried what?

11:47.400 --> 11:48.500
Now. Who the hell are you two?

11:48.600 --> 11:50.300
I'm agent skouris. This is agent baldwin.

11:50.400 --> 11:51.600
We're with ntac.

11:51.700 --> 11:52.400
Great.

11:52.500 --> 11:53.400
You got here just in time.

11:53.500 --> 11:54.700
Yeah. Cops let her go.

11:54.800 --> 11:58.400
You can take her to quarantine or stick her back in jail.

11:58.500 --> 12:00.300
