12:00.400 --> 12:02.800
She's a 4400.isn't she?

12:02.900 --> 12:06.200
She should never have been allowed 
back in this school in the first place.

12:06.300 --> 12:08.200
According to the preliminary exams.

12:08.300 --> 12:10.500
None of the kids showed any signs of abuse.

12:10.600 --> 12:12.300
No marks. No bruises?

12:12.400 --> 12:13.600
No physical signs. At any rate.

12:13.700 --> 12:16.200
So what are we talking about? Some kind of mental abuse?

12:16.300 --> 12:17.800
Personally. I'm not convinced it's abuse at all.

12:17.900 --> 12:20.400
But there's no denying that some of 
her students have been changed.

12:20.500 --> 12:21.300
Changed?

12:21.400 --> 12:23.100
In what way?

12:34.600 --> 12:36.700
That was beautiful.

12:36.900 --> 12:38.000
I guess.

12:38.100 --> 12:41.900
You're telling me two weeks ago 
you'd never played a violin.

12:42.000 --> 12:44.000
Never even touched one.

12:44.400 --> 12:50.700
Hey. I only took this class 'cause
art appreciation's supposed to be a guaranteed "A.

12:50.800 --> 12:53.700
