14:10.800 --> 14:14.300
I just find what's already inside them and help bring it out.

14:14.400 --> 14:16.400
How do you do that?

14:17.300 --> 14:18.900
I study them.

14:19.000 --> 14:20.141
Sometimes.

14:20.142 --> 14:21.761
There's a light in their eyes.

14:22.100 --> 14:24.200
Like a tiny flame.

14:24.300 --> 14:25.600
And while I'm watching.

14:25.700 --> 14:27.600
It gets brighter.

14:27.700 --> 14:29.800
That's when I know there's something in them.

14:29.900 --> 14:32.500
Something beautiful.

14:32.600 --> 14:35.712
So this light. Have you seen it in anyone else?

14:36.300 --> 14:38.400
It doesn't seem to work with grownups.

14:38.500 --> 14:41.000
It doesn't work with every kid. Either.

14:41.100 --> 14:43.400
Like this one boy. Greg venner.

14:43.500 --> 14:44.600
I keep looking.

14:44.700 --> 14:45.900
But so far...

14:46.000 --> 14:49.400
I think his father's pretty adamant that you stop looking.

14:49.500 --> 14:51.300
Frank?

14:51.400 --> 14:52.700
I taught frank.

14:52.800 --> 14:55.800
He was one of my first students back in '72.

14:55.900 --> 14:56.900
The fact is.

14:57.000 --> 15:00.300
I probably taught half the parents who are out to get me.

15:00.400 --> 15:01.500
This is crazy.

15:01.600 --> 15:04.800
L... I haven't done anything wrong.

15:04.900 --> 15:07.000
I need to get back to my kids.

15:07.100 --> 15:09.200
The people who took me.

15:09.300 --> 15:13.200
It can't be an accident they gave me this wonderful gift.

15:13.300 --> 15:15.500
That's why they sent me back.

15:15.600 --> 15:17.800
To use it.

